* Microsoft Purview
** What it is
***_ Enterprise data governance service
***_ Cross-platform: on-prem, multi-cloud, SaaS
** Core Features
***_ Data discovery
***_ Data classification
***_ Lineage tracking
***_ Access governance
** Databricks Integration
*** Scanning
****_ Scan public & private networks
****_ Scan entire Unity Catalog metastore
****_ Or scan selective catalogs
****_ On-demand or scheduled scans
*** Metadata Extraction
****_ Metastore, catalogs, schemas
****_ Tables, views, columns
*** Classification
****_ Built-in classification rules
****_ Custom user-defined rules
****_ Identifies sensitive data
*** Lineage
****_ How data is transformed & moved
****_ Across systems and processes
** Also Supports
***_ Workspace-level Hive metastore
@endmindmap
